among us. I kind of hope that I'm wrong about a lot of this because I can't say that my world

03:15:22.800 --> 03:15:28.800
view is particularly uplifting, but in some sense, it doesn't matter if it's uplifting or not,

03:15:28.800 --> 03:15:36.480
science is about what's reality, what's out there, why is it this way? And I think there's beauty

03:15:36.480 --> 03:15:44.000
in that too. There's beauty in darkness. You write about life and death sort of at the biological

03:15:44.000 --> 03:15:51.680
